Resource Profile: Vital Signs: SpO2

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/VitalSignsSpO2 Version: 1.5.11
Active as of 2025-05-08 Computable Name: VitalSignsSpO2

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file GMRV VITAL MEASUREMENT (120.5) to us-core-pulse-oximetry.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usage:

  • CapabilityStatements using this Resource Profile: Lighthouse Clinical Health API and Lighthouse Patient Health API
  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
